{"tid":2435671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(有片）愛國西醫兒子無牌搞醫學美容","createTime":"2021-03-06T12:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T02:47:27.000Z","uid":301152,"like":185,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"15259f88d3de9a34edadaee77b17c1391036e29c","tid":2435671,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:06:05.000Z","msg":"直擊酒店打針｜<br />\n踢爆前西醫工會副會長兒子<br />\n無牌搞醫學美容<br />\n2021-03-06 | <br />\n壹週刊<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_777903_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_777903_0&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=fc639ca0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_777903_0&h=297c79e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_777903_0</a><br />\n(詳細內容click入去睇, 有片) <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(節錄)<br />\n<br />\n//《壹週刊》調查發現，一間名為「Beauty At Home」的醫學美容公司提供上門打美容針服務。<br />\n<br />\n涉事醫生為<span class=\"violet\">前西醫工會副會長江炎輝</span>兒子江俊威，及一名鍾姓女助手。二人涉嫌在未有申請牌照，包括公司牌照、商業登記及《私營醫療機構條例》下相關牌照或豁免書，在酒店為客人提供入侵性醫美療程，如注射肉毒桿菌、去斑針及埋線等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外科專科醫生江俊威(James)出生醫學世家，爸爸江炎輝(Albert)是行內著名兒科專科醫生，前西醫工會副會長。<br />\n<br />\n愛國的Albert去年武肺爆發期間，更有份代表西醫工會<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">送口罩去中聯辦</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76KoQBS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76KoQBS.png&h=be622392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">「Beauty At Home」網頁及專頁未有提供清楚聯絡方法<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wd1259U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwd1259U.png&h=87cf5f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyfLjvA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyfLjvA.png&h=6b2efd63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港美容監察發起人袁海文對醫美行業作簡單解構：「這種生意很好賺，所以為甚麼這麼多跨專業，甚至非專業也想分一杯羹。」並以實例講解：「只要願意放下從醫初衷，只是幫人打針，一個完成實習的醫生每月能賺<span class=\"x-large\">16-17萬</span>。」面對豐厚油水，而無論<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">醫委會、衛生署的消極執法</span></span>，不少業界醫生也表示「賺咗先算」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同業縱容　醫醫相衛<br />\n<br />\n袁海文分享成功向醫委會投訴違規醫生的經驗：「判停牌，但有緩刑，甚至累犯也是緩刑。」<br />\n<br />\n而<span class=\"red\">衛生署派控煙辦執法、警察把投訴分類為「雜項」</span>，亦讓袁海文深感無奈，直言並非要求立新例，只希望能跟隨現有條例執法，「醫生會怕失去牌照，但不執法的話，大家也不會怕。」//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"orange\"> 無牌、又冇聯絡電話地址<br />\n而且在酒店進行這種高風險美容療程<br />\n打得唔好、出咗事唔知可以搵邊個追究 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醫委會、衛生署、警方又消極執法"},{"pid":"721ad310df2b73bea0f0c0b1675b04a91c30c72a","tid":2435671,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:06:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd3dfb78b2b743b833f903c2c1e08625e629eb8","tid":2435671,"uid":4322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},{"pid":"e0c1f6436f576102767c4665ff456c5d5902b4e6","tid":2435671,"uid":301152,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年DR毒針事件<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDR醫療集團毒血針事故，也稱為DR毒針殺人案，是指2012年發生於香港的一宗醫學美容嚴重醫療事故，涉及有人將尚在試驗階段的CIK（細胞因子誘導的殺傷細胞）治癌醫療技術，用作美容保健用途。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事件為香港歷史上最嚴重的一宗醫學美容事故，<span class=\"violet\">造成<span class=\"large\">一人死亡、一人受傷及一人殘障</span>。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/LE6DKJ5DWJCP5DNGZTC6IXOKGI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FLE6DKJ5DWJCP5DNGZTC6IXOKGI%2F&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n2mu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=1a7b398f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201208%2FLE6DKJ5DWJCP5DNGZTC6IXOKGI%2F&h=1eface4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201208/LE6DKJ5DWJCP5DNGZTC6IXOKGI/</a><br />\nDR醫學美容誤殺案︱<br />\n女醫生被判監三年半 <br />\n截肢苦主嘆變活死人：便宜咗佢"},{"pid":"6628799793a119ac9c4eac18111fa8317be11a0c","tid":2435671,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd3dfb78b2b743b833f903c2c1e08625e629eb8","tid":2435671,"uid":4322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f8156f57ebc071b53fbb8a683f514b41931c03","tid":2435671,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:08:54.000Z","msg":"仲流過插鼻果班"},{"pid":"c5406a8404ab127308509a7b983ee36eb4be6dbe","tid":2435671,"uid":4322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6628799793a119ac9c4eac18111fa8317be11a0c","tid":2435671,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cd3dfb78b2b743b833f903c2c1e08625e629eb8","tid":2435671,"uid":4322,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:06:31.000Z","msg":"Pishhh"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:08:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"Hi sis <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1e5cc51aff660d8e7a64d48bf1b7c02a35e242","tid":2435671,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T12:09:41.000Z","msg":"大陸手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1bf2d17ec8bd94f00a9a242ce0eed9074353b